headline: Heineken: Growth Has Come At The Expense Of Profitability
summary: Heineken N.V.'s long-term growth faces pressure from slowing alcohol consumption and weak macro trends. Click for insights on HEINY valuation and future outlook.

headline: Winners And Losers Of Q1: PepsiCo (NASDAQ:PEP) Vs The Rest Of The Beverages, Alcohol, and Tobacco Stocks
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at PepsiCo (NASDAQ:PEP) and the best and worst performers in the beverages, alcohol, and tobacco industry.
